title: Eoghan Connolly
text:
Eoghan Connolly is an <a href="Republic%20of%20Ireland">Irish</a> sportsperson. He plays <a href="hurling">hurling</a> with his local club <a href="Cashel%20King%20Cormacs%20GAA">Cashel King Cormacs</a> and with the <a href="Tipperary%20GAA">Tipperary</a> senior inter-county team since <a href="2021%20Tipperary%20county%20hurling%20team%20season">2021</a>.
Career.
Connolly made his <a href="2021%20National%20Hurling%20League">league</a> debut on 13 June 2021 against <a href="Waterford%20GAA">Waterford</a> when he came on as a late substitute.
